{"tid":811334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實 香港人有咩野可以對自己既身份咁自豪","createTime":"2018-09-08T17:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T17:19:12.000Z","uid":203388,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1ea37b1467e64eca49618c2e98e57ef96050fa","tid":811334,"uid":203388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"成日都諗唔明<br />\n香港人 永遠淨係識踩呢樣踩個樣 例如香港音樂 運動 明星等等 <br />\n好多人都去左中國到發展 但諗深一層 佢地會去中國發展 其實都只不過係因為中國比到香港比唔到既野 例如 人氣 錢 工作量 資源 等等<br />\n真係好想知點解 大家冇付出過 就要屌鳩人親中 我都對中國反感架 但無可厚非既係 中國比到既野比香港多好多<br />\n不如大家諗下 點解唔付出 但有資格批評<br />\n又唔擺放資源 又希望人地做到好好 點解咁on9"},{"pid":"fac342eaab8cd0bfc0f2413d76e498c2588a735e","tid":811334,"uid":195364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你係00後新港人"},{"pid":"3c9974224a3d13bc60f2770b107631b3366430d8","tid":811334,"uid":203388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac342eaab8cd0bfc0f2413d76e498c2588a735e","tid":811334,"uid":195364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你係00後新港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42183c4eece0477980cf3d3f791601bd42d0d3ae","tid":811334,"uid":195364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9974224a3d13bc60f2770b107631b3366430d8","tid":811334,"uid":203388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac342eaab8cd0bfc0f2413d76e498c2588a735e","tid":811334,"uid":195364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你係00後新港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"果時樂壇某班人玩杯葛玩死香港樂壇 你唔係唔知下話"},{"pid":"7594fbe24417c7ef0efd70d91362a8b46afda574","tid":811334,"uid":203388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42183c4eece0477980cf3d3f791601bd42d0d3a